WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.149
Good morning, family. I'm excited to be

00:00:02.159 --> 00:00:05.070
with you all. I just did a prayer video,

00:00:05.070 --> 00:00:05.080
and

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:07.590
this came out of

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.749
that prayer time. I saw a church when I

00:00:10.759 --> 00:00:12.709
was praying,

00:00:12.709 --> 00:00:12.719
and

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:15.910
it

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.429
was an old

00:00:18.429 --> 00:00:18.439
country-looking

00:00:18.439 --> 00:00:20.910
church with an old country steeple

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:23.310
on it. The church was completely

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:25.910
blacked out—the lights were off,

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:28.910
everybody was

00:00:28.910 --> 00:00:28.920
asleep—and

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:32.269
in the steeple, there

00:00:32.269 --> 00:00:32.279
were

00:00:32.279 --> 00:00:36.150
these massive gold bells that were

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:39.389
glowing with the glory of God.

00:00:39.399 --> 00:00:42.350
They looked like they were shiny; there

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:44.990
was a shininess all over these bells, and

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.709
I heard the Lord say, 'I'm going to do one

00:00:49.719 --> 00:00:54.470
more push, one more chance of a

00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:54.480
wakeup.'I

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:57.630
saw the bells ringing, and He said,

00:00:57.640 --> 00:01:00.029
'I'm going to wake up the church, and I'm going to

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:02.670
give

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:05.509
one more

00:01:05.509 --> 00:01:05.519
call.'When

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:07.469
I was praying

00:01:07.469 --> 00:01:07.479
and

00:01:07.479 --> 00:01:10.149
interceding, I was asking,

00:01:10.159 --> 00:01:12.390
'Lord, what does it mean?'And He said, 'The

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:15.030
bells are going to wake up the church;

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:17.630
I'm doing one more

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:17.640
push.'He

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:19.590
said it would be just as in the days of Noah.

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:21.870
Then He said to me, 'As in the days of

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.510
Noah, Brandon, so will it be when the Son

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:27.510
of Man returns.'He said,

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:31.390
'The door to the ark is about to close.

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:35.389
There's one more call,

00:01:35.399 --> 00:01:38.670
one more opportunity to get on the boat

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:41.030
before it's too late, before the Great

00:01:41.030 --> 00:01:41.040
Tribulation—one

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:44.270
more

00:01:44.270 --> 00:01:44.280
push.'I'm

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:48.389
telling you all that I

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:52.149
felt I wanted to weep about it

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.950
because there's

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:59.190
no time left; Jesus is coming.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:01.389
It's like whenever I'm hearing Him

00:02:01.399 --> 00:02:03.709
say that, you know, there's a lot of times

00:02:03.719 --> 00:02:05.709
it could be years, it could be days, it

00:02:05.719 --> 00:02:08.389
could be this year. I told

00:02:08.399 --> 00:02:11.309
everybody in the prayer video

00:02:11.319 --> 00:02:14.430
that Paul Begley did a video

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:17.750
tonight about the red

00:02:17.750 --> 00:02:17.760
heifer.

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:23.190
The Jews have built a

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:23.200
ramp—that

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:26.470
was on CBS and they televised

00:02:26.470 --> 00:02:26.480
it—with

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:28.589
an altar on there

00:02:28.599 --> 00:02:31.790
to sacrifice the heifer. Paul Begley told

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:34.550
everybody that they have

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.869
not done this sacrifice for over

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:39.630
2,000

00:02:39.640 --> 00:02:43.110
years, and that this

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:45.390
is the 10th time for them to do it.

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:50.270
Well, 800 years ago,

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:54.070
there was a prophecy from an old Rabbi

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:56.470
that there would be

00:02:56.480 --> 00:03:00.030
one more red heifer sacrificed and

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:01.830
that it would be the same year that

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:04.550
Jesus came. I asked Him even in

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:07.270
prayer time, 'Lord, shake the church; let

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:07.280
them

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:09.390
wake up one more time. Let's have one

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:12.710
more push for souls, one more

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:15.869
Great Harvest of souls, and then come

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:19.990
back and get us.'I know that people

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.110
are asleep; there's a lot of people

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:26.190
that need that shake to say, 'Get up,

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:29.149
Jesus is coming.'I pray that

00:03:29.159 --> 00:03:32.470
this video is an urgency wakeup

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:35.589
call to you all to hear that Jesus is

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:37.949
coming. The bells are going to

00:03:37.959 --> 00:03:40.309
