00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:42.830
telling you all that Jesus Christ

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:46.110
is coming. Are you on the boat

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:48.550
today?

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:53.550
The Lord told me just like it

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:56.229
was in the days of Noah, so will it be.

00:03:56.239 --> 00:03:58.069
I'm sure Noah was out there telling

00:03:58.079 --> 00:04:01.350
everybody, 'The rain's coming, folks, the

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:03.110
rain's coming,'and they mocked him and

00:04:03.110 --> 00:04:03.120
