00:04:07.390 --> 00:04:07.400
again.'The

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:10.830
rain's coming, the rain's coming, the great

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:14.069
flood's coming—it's coming, and everybody

00:04:14.079 --> 00:04:16.229
get on the boat as quickly as possible.

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:17.870
All the animals

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:20.150
